        "description": "<note> <p>This is the latest version of <b>AWS WAF</b>, named AWS WAFV2, released in November, 2019. For information, including how to migrate your AWS WAF resources from the prior release, see the <a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/waf/latest/developerguide/waf-chapter.html\">AWS WAF Developer Guide</a>. </p> </note> <p>Specifies a single rule to exclude from the rule group. Excluding a rule overrides its action setting for the rule group in the web ACL, setting it to <code>COUNT</code>. This effectively excludes the rule from acting on web requests. </p>"
